    "description": "<strong>《地牢猎人》是一款节奏非常快的Roguelike地牢探索游戏。<br>我们的特色：</strong><br><br><strong>简单又刺激的动作体验</strong><br>《地牢猎人》的操作非常简单，三位猎手会自动攻击进入射程的敌人。同时，可以通过移动积攒能量，然后选择适当时机手动释放威力更高的技能。当然，猎手们也可以利用灵活的步法闪避地牢内未知的凶险，只不过每一次主动躲闪都会消耗能量。相信聪明的你在任何情况下都能做出最出色的判断。<br><br><strong>法师、刺客、弓箭手的三人小队</strong><br>玩弄冰火，擅长高额群攻法术的魔法师；拥有超远射程，擅长多方向高频率打击敌人的弓箭手；隐身潜行，悄然出现在目标背后一招制敌的刺客。三种不同风格的职业战中即时切换，根据个人喜好或是地牢特征打造自己专属玩法，配合局内随机出现的职业强化，每次探索都能获得截然不同的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/e06fd6cd86435dc2e4d56319b701d5f2.poster.avif?t=1722569737\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/e06fd6cd86435dc2e4d56319b701d5f2.webm?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/e06fd6cd86435dc2e4d56319b701d5f2.mp4?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/f53b81d058964058028d017966b0ebff.poster.avif?t=1722569737\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/f53b81d058964058028d017966b0ebff.webm?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/f53b81d058964058028d017966b0ebff.mp4?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/ae9a5884cf9e3a4ebe0a977d4f1e91c1.poster.avif?t=1722569737\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/ae9a5884cf9e3a4ebe0a977d4f1e91c1.webm?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/ae9a5884cf9e3a4ebe0a977d4f1e91c1.mp4?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>局外职业养成&amp;局内随机增益</strong><br>开启隐藏在地牢角落的宝箱，可以获得提升猎手实力的道具。优先培养喜欢的职业，亦或是均衡发展全凭你的选择。同时地牢内大多数关卡还存在为猎手们提供增益的地点，我们称其为“赐福”。靠近赐福点，你可以从三项增益中选择最符合当前利益的一项，其中更包含职业限定的增益效果。这些效果不但会使特定职业打出更高的伤害，甚至可以改变玩法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/7cf25e155ebe6bb297a634ed22fd3ce7.poster.avif?t=1722569737\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/7cf25e155ebe6bb297a634ed22fd3ce7.webm?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038840/extras/7cf25e155ebe6bb297a634ed22fd3ce7.mp4?t=1722569737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>更多惊喜等你进入地牢，亲身探索。感谢各位的支持与喜爱，希望我们的游戏给大家带来快乐。",
